WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:middle
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:01:34.310 --> 00:01:37.340
<b>Under Siege</b>

3
00:01:37.340 --> 00:01:41.250
Allied forces!
Let's take shelter in the castle for now!

4
00:01:41.250 --> 00:01:42.920
All right, hurry up!

5
00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:44.650
Yeah, I wanna go in!

6
00:01:44.650 --> 00:01:47.920
Fire Tank Pirates! Cover them!

7
00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:49.250
– Rero !
– Yes, sir!

8
00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:52.690
Damn!

9
00:02:01.980 --> 00:02:05.330
Bege! I saw it with my own eyes!

10
00:02:05.330 --> 00:02:08.210
I can't believe you were
plotting to assassinate Mama!

11
00:02:08.210 --> 00:02:11.760
Was that his plan from the very beginning?!

12
00:02:13.010 --> 00:02:15.510
Get inside the castle-rero !

13
00:02:15.510 --> 00:02:18.620
Rook: Cannon Preparation!

14
00:02:21.340 --> 00:02:23.690
Cannon Firing!

15
00:02:26.060 --> 00:02:28.260
So cool!

16
00:02:28.260 --> 00:02:30.990
It's a robot! A robot castle!

17
00:02:30.990 --> 00:02:33.130
How can you be excited at a time like this?!

18
00:02:33.530 --> 00:02:36.970
How long can we hold out?

19
00:02:41.840 --> 00:02:44.140
This is killing my eardrums!

20
00:02:48.930 --> 00:02:50.050
Mochi ?

21
00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:04.130
Is that...

22
00:03:04.130 --> 00:03:06.700
the Tamate Box?!

23
00:03:09.970 --> 00:03:11.130
All right!

24
00:03:11.130 --> 00:03:13.770
W-What the hell is this?

25
00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:22.180
Who dares mess with the Great Gastino?!

26
00:03:30.060 --> 00:03:31.690
Big Brother!

27
00:03:31.690 --> 00:03:33.790
He's gonna kill me!

28
00:03:38.330 --> 00:03:42.400
Big Brother! Thank you!

29
00:03:44.490 --> 00:03:46.140
Let's go!

30
00:03:49.170 --> 00:03:51.140
I won't let you go!

31
00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:56.820
Cover them-rero ! Hurry-rero !

32
00:04:05.250 --> 00:04:06.990
Nami!

33
00:04:06.990 --> 00:04:09.860
I'll squeeze you to death!

34
00:04:09.860 --> 00:04:11.060
Nami-san !

35
00:04:11.060 --> 00:04:12.360
Nami!

36
00:04:13.830 --> 00:04:16.770
We're gonna fight you!

37
00:04:22.570 --> 00:04:24.510
Ach-ouch!

38
00:04:25.180 --> 00:04:28.450
Ouch, ouch! It's hot!

39
00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:28.460
You won't get away now!

40
00:04:28.460 --> 00:04:30.080
Chobro!

41
00:04:33.090 --> 00:04:35.120
Jinni!

42
00:05:19.230 --> 00:05:23.070
Let's go, Germa 66!

43
00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:40.860
You annoying bastards!

44
00:06:43.180 --> 00:06:45.680
All of you, burn to death!

45
00:06:54.190 --> 00:06:56.260
I-Is that...?!

46
00:07:14.380 --> 00:07:16.620
Germa's science.

47
00:07:16.620 --> 00:07:21.720
So that's what their memory armor looks like!
It's even flameproof!

48
00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:26.060
I'll just immobilize them with my candy again!

49
00:07:26.860 --> 00:07:29.030
Candy Wave!

50
00:08:00.050 --> 00:08:02.790
You obnoxious fleas!

51
00:08:17.860 --> 00:08:22.010
You're pretty big,
but that doesn't mean you're tough.

52
00:09:05.490 --> 00:09:06.730
Nami-san !

53
00:09:07.970 --> 00:09:10.200
Are you guys okay?!

54
00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:11.360
I am!

55
00:09:12.210 --> 00:09:13.390
Sanji-kun !

56
00:09:13.390 --> 00:09:15.770
I'm glad that you're okay, Nami-san !

57
00:09:18.380 --> 00:09:20.440
Gum-Gum...

58
00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:23.280
Jet Whip!

59
00:09:23.280 --> 00:09:24.600
Luffy!

60
00:09:24.600 --> 00:09:27.450
– Hurry up!
– This way!

61
00:09:28.680 --> 00:09:31.720
We should retreat as well-rero !

62
00:09:49.810 --> 00:09:53.810
Well, well, this is the Tamate Box, a legendary hidden treasure.

63
00:09:53.810 --> 00:09:58.520
Nobody will see me this far away from the action!
I love the current chaotic situation!

64
00:09:58.520 --> 00:10:03.550
I'll take this opportunity to replace what's inside...

65
00:10:43.960 --> 00:10:46.120
This is our last chance!

66
00:10:48.540 --> 00:10:50.630
Cannon Firing!

67
00:10:56.830 --> 00:10:58.140
Damn!

68
00:10:58.540 --> 00:11:00.400
Candy Wall!

69
00:11:01.080 --> 00:11:02.840
Perospero!

70
00:11:02.840 --> 00:11:05.250
Oh, that hurts...

71
00:11:05.250 --> 00:11:08.310
So is Germa working with you, too?

72
00:11:09.090 --> 00:11:12.380
I hope you bastards are ready
for what's coming to you.

73
00:11:12.380 --> 00:11:15.850
You won't be laughing for long!

74
00:11:24.100 --> 00:11:26.640
Rook: Movement!

75
00:11:44.050 --> 00:11:48.050
We'll shoot her in the back
until we're out of ammo!

76
00:11:49.220 --> 00:11:51.690
Time to die, Big Mom!

77
00:11:52.700 --> 00:11:53.430
Cannon...

78
00:11:54.590 --> 00:11:55.930
Firing!

79
00:11:58.680 --> 00:12:00.370
What just happened?!

80
00:12:01.150 --> 00:12:05.510
Father, our left-side cannons were destroyed!

81
00:12:05.510 --> 00:12:09.070
And the rest of them
have been jammed with mochi !

82
00:12:09.070 --> 00:12:11.580
We can't fire them anymore!

83
00:12:15.450 --> 00:12:18.020
K-Katakuri!

84
00:12:18.250 --> 00:12:22.490
<b>Inside Big Father</b>

85
00:12:22.490 --> 00:12:26.020
I've got some bad news for everyone in the castle...

86
00:12:39.690 --> 00:12:43.980
Big Father's limbs are trapped under candy!

87
00:12:45.410 --> 00:12:48.780
We can't even move anymore!

88
00:12:50.410 --> 00:12:55.440
We're surrounded by Emperor Big Mom's pirate crew

89
00:12:55.440 --> 00:13:00.990
and must now hole ourselves up
in the castle while we're under siege!

90
00:13:02.080 --> 00:13:04.220
No...

91
00:13:20.910 --> 00:13:23.780
Anyone who steps out will die.

92
00:13:25.980 --> 00:13:28.780
Just come out already!

93
00:13:30.110 --> 00:13:33.190
How could you let them use you like that?

94
00:13:33.190 --> 00:13:35.860
I-I'm the victim here, Big Brother!

95
00:13:35.860 --> 00:13:39.100
Just hurry up and destroy
each and every one of them!

96
00:13:41.370 --> 00:13:45.100
Poison?
That woman is quite troublesome...

97
00:14:02.390 --> 00:14:03.760
There you are!

98
00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:07.810
You're amazing, Bege!
You're able to transform into a huge castle!

99
00:14:07.810 --> 00:14:09.790
The Castle-Castle Fruit is so cool!

100
00:14:09.790 --> 00:14:13.670
This isn't the time for praise!
Think about the situation we're in!

101
00:14:13.670 --> 00:14:14.830
Dammit...

102
00:14:14.830 --> 00:14:18.600
We planned this assassination for over a year,

103
00:14:18.600 --> 00:14:20.540
and it ended in failure!

104
00:14:20.540 --> 00:14:24.920
We've never failed to assassinate someone before...

105
00:14:25.790 --> 00:14:29.700
In the end, an emperor proved
to be out of our league...

106
00:14:29.700 --> 00:14:31.880
What should we do now?

107
00:14:31.880 --> 00:14:36.620
We don't have much time left.
Here's why.

108
00:14:36.620 --> 00:14:39.960
Listen carefully, you guys!

109
00:14:39.960 --> 00:14:43.600
I am this castle.
It's strong, but it isn't invincible.

110
00:14:43.600 --> 00:14:48.870
If the castle gets destroyed, I die. 
Which means the castle disappears,

111
00:14:48.870 --> 00:14:52.860
and then all of you will be tossed out there
to be the prey for those monsters!

112
00:14:52.860 --> 00:14:54.340
Prey?!

113
00:15:08.350 --> 00:15:11.260
I'll never forgive them...

114
00:15:13.660 --> 00:15:14.830
Mama!

115
00:15:16.690 --> 00:15:19.830
I can feel Mama's anger...

116
00:15:31.010 --> 00:15:35.350
It's hell out there, and it's hell in here.

117
00:15:35.350 --> 00:15:37.680
We're in dire straits!

118
00:15:37.680 --> 00:15:42.050
Don't blame me, Bege! Those launchers featured state-of-the-art, world-class...

119
00:15:48.590 --> 00:15:50.830
– W-What was that?
– Father!

120
00:15:50.830 --> 00:15:52.580
Hey, Bege! What's wrong?!

121
00:15:52.580 --> 00:15:54.630
Honey, are you okay?!

122
00:15:58.140 --> 00:15:59.540
Could it be...

123
00:16:00.570 --> 00:16:01.940
Look outside!

124
00:16:01.940 --> 00:16:03.310
What?

125
00:16:03.310 --> 00:16:05.020
Outside?

126
00:16:10.820 --> 00:16:12.780
You bastards!

127
00:16:12.780 --> 00:16:14.950
Come out!

128
00:16:16.950 --> 00:16:19.030
Bege!

129
00:16:19.030 --> 00:16:21.060
Straw Hat!

130
00:16:22.330 --> 00:16:24.200
I'm scared!

131
00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:26.620
She's looking at us!

132
00:16:27.810 --> 00:16:31.980
Big Mom came to her senses!

133
00:16:41.080 --> 00:16:44.250
All of you, come out of the castle!

134
00:16:44.250 --> 00:16:46.680
Show yourselves, you cowards!

135
00:16:49.320 --> 00:16:51.160
Honey!

136
00:16:51.160 --> 00:16:52.560
Father!

137
00:16:52.560 --> 00:16:55.830
So you betrayed me?

138
00:16:55.830 --> 00:16:57.540
Bege!

139
00:16:59.750 --> 00:17:03.090
Honey! Stay with me!

140
00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:08.840
I'm scared!

141
00:17:08.840 --> 00:17:12.940
Come out, Bege! Straw Hat!

142
00:17:16.350 --> 00:17:17.330
Bege!

143
00:17:17.930 --> 00:17:19.890
Hold Pez!

144
00:17:26.020 --> 00:17:27.960
Come out!

145
00:17:27.960 --> 00:17:30.190
Wait!

146
00:17:30.190 --> 00:17:34.200
Mama! It's me!
Bege is my husband! We had a child together!

147
00:17:34.200 --> 00:17:36.700
Please just forgive him and let us go!

148
00:17:36.700 --> 00:17:38.790
Chiffon!

149
00:17:39.620 --> 00:17:43.210
You still look just like Lola!

150
00:17:44.280 --> 00:17:45.280
She's going to attack!

151
00:17:45.280 --> 00:17:46.280
Watch out!

152
00:17:46.280 --> 00:17:47.510
Get back, Chiffon!

153
00:17:47.510 --> 00:17:48.650
Madam!

154
00:17:48.650 --> 00:17:50.680
Mama! Please!

155
00:17:51.050 --> 00:17:55.550
I told you not to show that face around here!

156
00:18:02.440 --> 00:18:04.220
That was close...

157
00:18:04.220 --> 00:18:05.430
Are you okay?

158
00:18:05.430 --> 00:18:07.170
Madam!

159
00:18:07.170 --> 00:18:11.170
Are you in on this assassination plot too, Chiffon?!

160
00:18:11.170 --> 00:18:14.480
You won't live to eat tomorrow's snacks,
that's for sure!

161
00:18:14.480 --> 00:18:15.810
Mama!

162
00:18:19.010 --> 00:18:24.380
If she tears down the castle and Bege dies,
then they'll all appear right in front of us!

163
00:18:24.380 --> 00:18:26.370
Don't let a single one of them escape!

164
00:18:26.370 --> 00:18:30.190
The Fire Tank Pirates... the Straw Hat crew...

165
00:18:30.190 --> 00:18:33.430
Plus, Jinbe and Germa 66!

166
00:18:33.430 --> 00:18:37.660
They ruined the wedding
and the tea party!

167
00:18:37.660 --> 00:18:40.550
I can't believe they underestimated us.

168
00:18:40.550 --> 00:18:43.740
We need to wring them out
and make an example of them to the world.

169
00:18:43.740 --> 00:18:46.100
Come out!

170
00:18:47.910 --> 00:18:49.650
Bege!

171
00:18:50.110 --> 00:18:51.780
Honey!

172
00:18:55.160 --> 00:18:56.650
Are you okay?

173
00:18:56.650 --> 00:18:59.720
Damn, that old bag!

174
00:19:01.950 --> 00:19:06.840
Big Father can take a cannon blast
without a scratch,

175
00:19:06.840 --> 00:19:09.060
but it can't defend against her!

176
00:19:09.060 --> 00:19:12.300
I've gotta go out there and kick her ass!

177
00:19:12.300 --> 00:19:13.500
No, Luffy!

178
00:19:13.500 --> 00:19:14.710
Chopper, grab him!

179
00:19:14.710 --> 00:19:16.030
Okay!

180
00:19:19.680 --> 00:19:22.740
What the?! Hey! Let go of me!

181
00:19:22.740 --> 00:19:24.890
Hey, Chopper! Let go of me!

182
00:19:24.890 --> 00:19:28.100
Luffy! Don't get carried away!

183
00:19:28.100 --> 00:19:32.820
We're here to get Sanji-kun back,
remember?!

184
00:19:32.820 --> 00:19:35.600
We got the poneglyph copies we needed,

185
00:19:35.600 --> 00:19:39.090
and we even helped Sanji-kun rescue his family!

186
00:19:39.090 --> 00:19:42.560
We've completed our mission!

187
00:19:42.560 --> 00:19:47.100
Instead of fighting, you should be helping us
come up with an escape plan!

188
00:19:47.100 --> 00:19:52.000
If we intended on fighting her, we would've
brought Zoro and the rest! Isn't that right?!

189
00:19:52.000 --> 00:19:54.970
Luffy-san, Nami-san is right.

190
00:19:54.970 --> 00:19:59.610
We made it this far
because we came in such a small group.

191
00:19:59.610 --> 00:20:03.850
Let's escape and meet up
with Zoro-san and the others in Wano!

192
00:20:07.900 --> 00:20:09.320
Bege!

193
00:20:09.320 --> 00:20:10.470
Father!

194
00:20:10.470 --> 00:20:12.360
Bege!

195
00:20:14.590 --> 00:20:16.530
See?! Bege is...

196
00:20:17.240 --> 00:20:19.430
What should we do then?!

197
00:20:19.430 --> 00:20:22.740
Bege is risking his life for us!

198
00:20:28.910 --> 00:20:31.080
Dammit...

199
00:20:31.080 --> 00:20:34.910
My plans are in utter ruin...

200
00:20:35.610 --> 00:20:39.370
so I'm definitely not willing to sit idly by
as you all relish in your success!

201
00:20:39.370 --> 00:20:44.500
Wait a minute, Bege-san !
You can't drag us down with you!

202
00:20:44.500 --> 00:20:46.700
I did what I was supposed to do!

203
00:20:46.700 --> 00:20:49.550
Give me back my heart this instant!

204
00:20:50.340 --> 00:20:52.630
Drag you down...?

205
00:20:52.630 --> 00:20:55.100
That's not a bad idea.

206
00:20:55.510 --> 00:20:59.310
Like I said from the start,
I don't care what happens to any of you guys!

207
00:21:09.530 --> 00:21:11.190
But...

208
00:21:11.190 --> 00:21:15.780
my precious subordinates...

209
00:21:15.780 --> 00:21:18.240
and my beloved wife and son are here.

210
00:21:21.100 --> 00:21:25.030
And there's no way I can let them die!

211
00:21:25.030 --> 00:21:26.460
Honey!

212
00:21:26.460 --> 00:21:28.930
Father!

213
00:21:33.200 --> 00:21:34.060
Bege!

214
00:21:38.400 --> 00:21:41.710
There's only one way...

215
00:21:43.950 --> 00:21:46.610
to make sure everyone survives!

216
00:21:46.610 --> 00:21:47.740
Only one?!

217
00:21:47.740 --> 00:21:49.390
What is it?!

218
00:21:53.140 --> 00:21:55.890
Come out!

219
00:21:55.890 --> 00:21:58.690
I'm gonna destroy it!

220
00:22:00.670 --> 00:22:03.070
It won't last much longer...

221
00:22:03.070 --> 00:22:06.110
Get ready to attack anytime now...

222
00:22:07.070 --> 00:22:09.510
I can crush them with this!

223
00:22:09.510 --> 00:22:11.740
Let's get rid of...

224
00:22:12.060 --> 00:22:13.910
every last one of them!

225
00:22:16.610 --> 00:22:21.420
Hurry up and come out!
Then, I'll trap all of you in my mirror dimension!

226
00:22:24.860 --> 00:22:28.530
The only way to survive... That is...

227
00:22:28.530 --> 00:22:35.230
This room inside Big Father...
is actually inside my body.

228
00:22:36.790 --> 00:22:37.340
Hey!

229
00:22:37.340 --> 00:22:39.600
Don't panic!

230
00:22:41.640 --> 00:22:44.640
No matter how much I'm attacked...

231
00:22:45.260 --> 00:22:49.470
if Big Father leans or falls over,

232
00:22:50.020 --> 00:22:53.820
I'm the only one who will get hurt.

233
00:22:53.820 --> 00:22:58.230
As long as you guys are here,
you won't get hurt at all.

234
00:22:58.230 --> 00:23:02.950
– Come to think of it...
– It's only Bege-san who is suffering.

235
00:23:04.600 --> 00:23:07.530
We can hear Big Mom's voice...

236
00:23:09.500 --> 00:23:12.270
but it's still calm in here.

237
00:23:15.420 --> 00:23:17.490
That's right...

238
00:23:17.490 --> 00:23:22.710
And that won't change even
if I change back into my human form.

239
00:23:22.710 --> 00:23:27.570
Listen... I'm going to return to being human
with you all still inside!

240
00:23:27.570 --> 00:23:32.160
Then, Caesar will pick me up and fly us to safety!

241
00:23:32.160 --> 00:23:36.260
If all goes well, we'll get out of this mess.

242
00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:41.800
Hey! How dare you try and put my life in danger
without even asking me, you bastard!

243
00:23:41.800 --> 00:23:44.040
That's a suicide mission!

244
00:23:44.040 --> 00:23:49.600
They'll pump us full of lead as soon as we leave! That plan's chance of success is zero!

245
00:23:49.600 --> 00:23:51.740
Many of them use armanent haki!

246
00:23:51.740 --> 00:23:54.610
Even if I turn into gas,
I can't defend against them!

247
00:23:54.610 --> 00:23:56.980
Let me ask you something.

248
00:23:58.450 --> 00:23:59.690
Sanji,

249
00:24:02.230 --> 00:24:04.780
why did you save us?

250
00:24:06.440 --> 00:24:11.430
We're your enemies that fell right into their trap!

251
00:24:14.930 --> 00:24:18.810
Because my father would be sad...

252
00:24:19.970 --> 00:24:24.040
if I were still fixated on the hatred from my childhood...

253
00:24:26.860 --> 00:24:28.550
Please let me out!

254
00:24:28.550 --> 00:24:31.380
Dad! I'm sorry!

255
00:24:32.420 --> 00:24:36.490
I'm sorry that I was born weak!

256
00:24:36.490 --> 00:24:42.790
Help me, Dad!

257
00:24:45.760 --> 00:24:49.080
He would be astonished
that I had turned into such a small man

258
00:24:49.080 --> 00:24:53.570
that I would laugh off the death of my blood-family.

259
00:24:53.570 --> 00:24:58.140
Don't catch a cold.

260
00:24:58.140 --> 00:25:01.760
I don't want to live a life where I'll be too ashamed

261
00:25:01.760 --> 00:25:03.820
to face him!

262
00:25:08.380 --> 00:25:12.390
Don't ever admit that I'm your father...

263
00:25:12.390 --> 00:25:17.020
to even a single person!

264
00:25:20.900 --> 00:25:25.110
I do not want anyone
to learn of my shame!

265
00:25:25.570 --> 00:25:27.770
Do you understand?

266
00:25:31.210 --> 00:25:33.110
Thirteen years ago,

267
00:25:33.110 --> 00:25:38.550
I ran away from Germa, and Vinsmoke Sanji died at sea.

268
00:25:38.550 --> 00:25:41.290
And that is what you wanted.

269
00:25:52.930 --> 00:25:55.230
So admit it!

270
00:25:55.970 --> 00:26:00.600
You are not my father, Vinsmoke Judge!

271
00:26:01.370 --> 00:26:04.400
Don't ever show your face around us again!

272
00:26:28.400 --> 00:26:30.670
I understand.

273
00:26:30.670 --> 00:26:33.010
Then you have my word...

274
00:26:33.010 --> 00:26:35.270
I will never approach you...

275
00:26:35.270 --> 00:26:38.340
or the East Blue ever again!

276
00:26:45.350 --> 00:26:47.920
I already did my part!

277
00:26:47.920 --> 00:26:50.490
This wasn't part of the deal!

278
00:26:50.490 --> 00:26:55.020
If you don't do this, you're going to die anyway, Caesar!

279
00:26:56.830 --> 00:26:58.900
Open the gate!

280
00:27:00.360 --> 00:27:05.020
Gang Bege! Until Caesar Clown
carries you to safety through the air,

281
00:27:05.020 --> 00:27:08.020
Germa will serve to guard you!

282
00:27:08.020 --> 00:27:09.570
W-Wait a minute!

283
00:27:09.570 --> 00:27:12.300
What gives you the right
to decide what I should do?!

284
00:27:12.300 --> 00:27:15.880
Your high-handed attitude hasn't changed, Judge!

285
00:27:18.350 --> 00:27:22.050
Oh yeah... Germa can fly, too.

286
00:27:22.050 --> 00:27:23.950
Then... we'll leave you behind.

287
00:27:23.950 --> 00:27:25.420
That won't be a problem.

288
00:27:27.860 --> 00:27:30.860
All right, if we're trying to buy time, I'll...

289
00:27:31.430 --> 00:27:34.400
There's no need, Luffy.

290
00:27:33.360 --> 00:27:34.390
But...

291
00:27:56.590 --> 00:28:00.460
I do not need help from a failure!

292
00:28:02.750 --> 00:28:05.920
This is how they want to make amends.

293
00:28:07.260 --> 00:28:09.300
Wait, wait! Whoa-whoa!

294
00:28:09.300 --> 00:28:12.300
I never said I'd help, you fools!

295
00:28:12.700 --> 00:28:14.340
Caesar!

296
00:28:14.340 --> 00:28:16.310
Shut up and do it!

297
00:28:16.310 --> 00:28:18.880
Ouch!

298
00:28:18.880 --> 00:28:20.950
You'll pay for this!

299
00:28:24.420 --> 00:28:27.650
Come on out already!

300
00:28:27.650 --> 00:28:29.190
Bege!

301
00:28:38.210 --> 00:28:41.410
Germa! Commence the attack!
